items.title: Rubie s Star Wars Toy Halloween Costume Accessory
items.description: Complete your Star Wars costume with this officially licensed toy Ahsoka Tano lightsaber. You don t need to be Jedi apprentice during the clone wars to get yourself a sweet weapon like this. The green blade and detailed handle has a look of authenticity  and you don t have to battle the likes of Asajj Ventress  General Grievous  or Cad Bane to appreciate it. Slash through Empire Forces and Join the Jedi with the power of Ashoka s Lightsaber. Its Collapsible design seals firmly with a locking half ring for safety. When the battle is on  undo the ring and unsheath by holding firmly and swinging toward the ground leaving a few feet of room. Power up glowing radiate Green energy with the flip of a switch with Long Lasting LED lights.
